videos.description: Vavae Malepeai punches it in for a 1-yard score to give USC a 7-0 lead.
videos.headline: USC gets on the scoreboard first

videos.description: USC's Aca-Cedric Ware runs 26-yards down the sideline for a score.
videos.headline: Ware takes it 26 yards to the house

videos.description: Miscommunication with the USC offense results in the ball being snapped, fumbled and recovered by Arizona.
videos.headline: USC commits turnover on unexpected snap

videos.description: USC's Aca-Cedric Ware gets loose for his second rushing touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Ware breaks out for a 69 -yard TD run

videos.description: Arizona's Khalil Tate connects with Stanley Berryhill III for a 33-yard score.
videos.headline: Berryhill makes diving grab for Arizona TD

videos.description: Khalil Tate rolls out and finds Cedric Peterson in the back of the end zone for a 32-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Tate connects with Peterson for 32-yard TD
